com.hbm.devices.scan.announce

Class AnnounceParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hbm.devices.scan.announce.AnnounceParams
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class AnnounceParams
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The AnnounceParams describe the properties of the device, which contain information of the device itself (like uuid, name, type, etc), the NetSettings, router information the device is connected to and running services
    Since:
    1.0

        public Device getDevice()
        Gets the router specific information of an announce message.
        Returns:
        the device. It is guaranteed by the AnnounceDeserializer that only valid announces are forwarded through the chain of observers, so a null reference is never returned from this method.
